{"tid":1186858,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"上水官中一度倒掛五星旗　校方表示歉意","createTime":"2019-06-05T08:28:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-05T09:47:26.000Z","uid":39464,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"48363c87c696a1dc4d2cc77a4f1512a98fadcdce","tid":1186858,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T08:28:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190605/photo/bkn-20190605153830581-0605_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190605161429\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190605%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190605153830581-0605_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190605161429&h=0514b149&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上水官立中學倒掛五星旗。今晨(5日)8時許有市民途經校園，發現學校五星旗倒掛，至上午11時許，學校職員將五星旗掛正。 <br />\n<br />\n上水官立中學回覆東網查詢時表示，由於昨天(4日)下大雨，學校把五星旗收起，今晨再由校工掛起，但校工忙中有錯，犯下無心之失，學校發現情況後立即更正，對事件表示歉意，並稱日後會加倍留神，避免同類事件發生。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190605/bkn-20190605153830581-0605_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190605%2Fbkn-20190605153830581-0605_00822_001.html&d=bqe6r6CGoyJNILHzVVCKLzFPTz8k007NAABMmnbcnzw%3D&h=e4178d00\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190605/bkn-20190605153830581-0605_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"0a2bf7e602afaa27f3ce350c54e52dbbcfa86890","tid":1186858,"uid":201158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T08:29:34.000Z","msg":"校工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5adfbdd44eb6fd7edeb2e082757146eefa923d4c","tid":1186858,"uid":26389,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T08:32:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKv461.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKv461.jpg&h=fdcae085&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b4b7da79bf50bef3f645b624b60b087881b62bf6","tid":1186858,"uid":155095,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy"